```

## Test: student_001 — Student earned income exclusion ($500 ≤ $2,410 monthly limit): income reduced by $500 before standard exclusions. Result: (3000 - 500 - 20 - 65) × 0.5 = 1207.50

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestStudent001:
  result scope Exclusion_chain.ExclusionChainDecision

scope TestStudent001:
  definition result.gross_earned_income equals $3,000
  definition result.federal_exclusions equals $0
  definition result.eitc_exclusion equals $0
  definition result.irregular_earned_income equals $0
  definition result.student_earned_income equals $500
  definition result.student_monthly_limit equals $2,410
  definition result.non_needs_based_unearned_remainder equals $20
  definition result.impairment_work_expenses equals $0
  definition result.blind_work_expenses equals $0
  definition result.self_support_exclusion equals $0
  assertion (result.adjusted_earned_income = $1,207.50)
```

