## Test: full_chain_001 — All 10 exclusion steps applied: federal ($100), EITC ($200), irregular ($10), student ($300), $20 general, $65 earned, IRWE ($100), one-half, blind work ($50), self-support ($75). Result: 1977.50

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestFullChain001:
  result scope Exclusion_chain.ExclusionChainDecision

scope TestFullChain001:
  definition result.gross_earned_income equals $5,000
  definition result.federal_exclusions equals $100
  definition result.eitc_exclusion equals $200
  definition result.irregular_earned_income equals $10
  definition result.student_earned_income equals $300
  definition result.student_monthly_limit equals $2,410
  definition result.non_needs_based_unearned_remainder equals $20
  definition result.impairment_work_expenses equals $100
  definition result.blind_work_expenses equals $50
  definition result.self_support_exclusion equals $75
  assertion (result.adjusted_earned_income = $1,977.50)
```

